Package jchrest.domainSpecifics

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DomainSpecifics
    An interface for defining domain-specific methods.
    Fixation
    Represents the result of a Perceiver associated with a Chrest model focusing on a Square in a jchrest.lib.Scene.
    Scene
    Represents a 2D external environment that a CHREST model can "see" as a 2D ArrayList containing one SceneObject per coordinate.
    SceneObject
    Class that represents objects in a jchrest.lib.Scene.
